article.headline: Tyreese Watson hits winning shot, scores 16 to rally UL Monroe over Northwestern State 65-63
article.description: — Tyreese Watson hit a go-ahead jumper with 4 seconds left and finished with 16 points to rally UL Monroe to a 65-63 victory over Northwestern State on Friday night.
article.linkText: Tyreese Watson hits winning shot, scores 16 to rally UL Monroe over Northwestern State 65-63
article.story: NATCHITOCHES, La. -- — Tyreese Watson hit a go-ahead jumper with 4 seconds left and finished with 16 points to rally UL Monroe to a 65-63 victory over Northwestern State on Friday night. Watson shot 5 of 11 from the field and 5 of 6 from the free-throw line for the Warhawks (3-4). Jalen Bolden scored 13 points and added six rebounds. Makai Willis had 11 points. The Demons (2-4) were led by Addison Patterson, who recorded 16 points and eight assists. Jerald Colonel contributed 13 points, eight rebounds and five blocks. Jon Sanders had 13 points and four assists. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
